{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/store_page_title_1_-_chess_dungeons.png?t=1725286397\" /><br>Chess Dungeons is a Puzzle game that combines Chess mechanics and Sokoban-style gameplay for chess lovers and beginners.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/store_page_title_2_-_enter_the_dungeon.png?t=1725286397\" /><br>While featuring classic Chess gameplay, enjoy playing with models that give character to every single chess piece. Control your units and make sure you come out victorious.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/store_page_title_3_-_make_sacrifices.png?t=1725286397\" /><br>In classic Chess fashion, sometimes in order to advance, you must sacrifice your pieces to lure the enemy out and advance into the dungeon.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/store_page_title_4.5_-_two_modes.png?t=1725286397\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/store_page_title_4_-_kingslayer.png?t=1725286397\" /><br>Don't lose focus! Your goal is to slay the enemy's King. While other pieces can (and sometimes should!) be targeted, your main focus is to eliminate the King.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/kingslayer.gif?t=1725286397\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020080/extras/store_page_title_5_-_clear_the_board.png?t=1725286397\" /><br>A harder challenge! Don't just target the enemy King. Wipe out all of the black pieces!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020